        p Music can be a large part of our home life 50. We design and install audio systems that allow music to be listened to throughout the home. There are two basic types of whole house systems: multiroom and multiroom/multisource systems. Multiroom systems allow the same music source to be enjoyed throughout the home at the same time. Multiroom/Multisource systems allow the home to be divided into multiple listening areas. For example, while the kids are dancing to Radio Disney in the playroom, their mom could be listening to a podcast in the kitchen. Our systems are compatible with:

