        h3 Ultra Customizable
        p Our sophisticated systems offer more convenience 40. Providing separate channels of amplification and an intelligent controller for each zone allows maximum flexibility. It also eliminates potential impedance mismatching problems. We offer systems that will allow any single room to be turned on without having to worry about the last setting of the other room's volume controls. If desired, groups of rooms can also be turned on/off from that same, simple to use keypad. We offer systems from ADA, Control4, Crestron, Integra and RTI that can easily handle this, routing any centralized source to any room independently or simultaneously.

        h3 Meridian Multi-room
        p For more critical listening rooms, utilizing the Meridian multi-room feature with local sources is an ideal, high quality solution 45. An ADA, Control4, Crestron or RTI could still control the Meridian, but the signals would bypass their preamp, sending direct digital signals to the speakers for superior sound. Want the entire system to be at the Meridian quality? Meridian offers their proprietary "speakerlink" that sends their digital information throughout your home on shielded CAT5e wiring.

